#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Dutiyapathavīsutta → dutiyapaṭhavisuttaṃ (bj) | paṭhavī 2 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Dutiyapathavīsutta "
msgstr "6. The Earth (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.6:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāpathavī parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, ṭhapetvā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the great earth was worn away and eroded except for seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.6:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.6:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā mahāpathaviyā parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ yā vā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā avasiṭṭhā”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the great earth that has been worn away and eroded, or the seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds that are left?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn13.6:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, mahāpathaviyā, yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ; "
msgstr "“Sir, the great earth that has been worn away and eroded is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.6:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā avasiṭṭhā. "
msgstr "The seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.6:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti mahāpathaviyā parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā avasiṭṭhā”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the great earth that has been worn away and eroded, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.6:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done with is more …” "

msgctxt "sn13.6:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.6:2.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

